<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\crt\libc\ctype\toupper">toupper towupper</sample>
    <title>toupper towupper</title>
    <volume>C 运行库函数</volume>
    <routine_idx> ctype_idx.htm </routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>将一个给定的小写字符转换成大写字符。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <func_name>toupper</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>c</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>需要判断的整型值</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>
     <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <func_name>towupper</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>c</param_name>
               
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
        <para>toupper将给定整型值（英文字符的ascii值）c的一个拷贝转换为对应大写字符的ascii值，无错误返回。</para>
    </return>

    <remarks>
        <para>该函数将能够转换的小写字符转换为大写字符。</para>
    </remarks>

    <requirements>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>toupper</routine_name>
            <headerfile>ctype.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>twoupper</routine_name>
            <headerfile>ctype.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
    </requirements>

    <example>
<pre>
//==========================================================================
// Copyright (c) 2000-2008,  Elastos, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.
//==========================================================================

/* toupper.cpp: This program use toupper converts a english characters
 * string to a uppercase string.
 */

#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;
#include &lt;ctype.h&gt;

char msg[] = &quot;THESE letters will BE Capitals\n&quot;;
char *p;

int main()
{
    printf(&quot;%s&quot;, msg);

    /* Reverse case of message. */
    for (p = msg; *p; p++)
        putchar(toupper(*p));

    return 0;
}
</pre>
    </example>
<result>
THESE letters will BE Capitals
THESE LETTERS WILL BE CAPITALS
</result>



